# Tier-3 / G4 — tinyproxy FQDN allowlist (FilterDefaultDeny Yes ⇒ only these match).
# POSIX-extended regex, anchored, matched against the CONNECT host (FilterExtended Yes).
#
# Hostnames the claude CLI / Max-plan session need:
#   api.anthropic.com        — the Anthropic API (chat/messages). REQUIRED.
# The Max-plan subscription auth flow and the CLI's normal operation egress to
# api.anthropic.com. The two entries below also permit any *.anthropic.com sub-host in
# case the CLI uses a regional/edge API hostname under the same domain — review the
# CLI's actual egress (RUNBOOK Step 4 verify logs) and tighten to exactly the hosts seen.
#
# If telemetry/error-reporting must be allowed (OFF by default — keep it denied unless
# the CLI hard-fails without it), the candidate hosts would be statsig.anthropic.com and
# a sentry ingest host; do NOT add them unless verified necessary. Prefer disabling CLI
# telemetry over widening the allowlist.

^api\.anthropic\.com$
^([a-z0-9-]+\.)*anthropic\.com$
